Package it.polimi.ingsw.network

Class BeanTranslator

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.network.BeanTranslator
public class BeanTranslator extends Object
Translates from a LinkedTreeMap to a bean of the correct type This class is fairly fragile, as it needs updating every time an attribute name changes All translating methods in this class take a map from the gson serialization and return a bean of the associated type
